1
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:30,920
What's going on?

2
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:33,040
Where's my diamond?

3
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,760
I'm asking you where my diamond is!

4
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:36,840
Mr. Zhen,

5
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:38,120
didn't you take

6
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:39,560
the Heart of Black Diamond?

7
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:42,040
So it was a distraction.

8
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:58,000
I don't know anything.

9
00:00:58,280 --> 00:00:59,440
I didn't see anything.

10
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,320
The Heart of Black Diamond

11
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:34,640
is missing.

12
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:37,440
How are you going to balance the books?

13
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,240
Heart of Black Diamond

14
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:43,400
must have been stolen by Hao Feng's brother.

15
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,520
Hao Feng's brother?

16
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,320
No way, Boss Zhen.

17
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,280
Isn't he dead?

18
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,480
We saw it with our own eyes.

19
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,560
Did you forget?

20
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,320
The organization has investigated.

21
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:05,920
He's not Hao Feng's brother.

22
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,680
He is Hao Feng.

23
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:11,920
Impossible.

24
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,720
Hao Feng is dead.

25
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,920
Hao Feng has been dead for a long time.

26
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,920
I saw it with my own eyes.

27
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,320
His ashes were scattered in the river.

28
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,920
You're so sure.

29
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,520
Then recall what you did

30
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:27,720
about that thing

31
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:29,240
a year ago.

32
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,640
I did as the organization asked.

33
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,520
I...

34
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,160
I did it perfectly.

35
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,200
I didn't expect you to be so heavy.

36
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:01,920
Hao Feng.

37
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,960
Relax.

38
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,360
Hurry up.

39
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,000
Right.

40
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,560
Remember my face.

41
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,880
Perfect.

42
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,560
His head is pierced.

43
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,560
He's dead as a doornail.

44
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,480
300 million.

45
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,600
You took

46
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,960
300 million crowdfunding funds all by yourself.

47
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:13,000
Hao Feng took the blame for you.

48
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,160
Boss Zhen.

49
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,720
what a good deal.

50
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,760
The organization promised me

51
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,480
that I could keep this money.

52
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:20,800
But...

53
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,760
But I can give it back.

54
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:22,480
I can give it to you.

55
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,000
Please let me go.

56
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,360
Please let me go.

57
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:25,960
Okay?

58
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,560
You have no money now.

59
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:29,880
How can you...

60
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,200
You know so many secrets of the organization.

61
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,680
Do you think you can live anymore?

62
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:36,680
Ex...

63
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,600
Exper...

64
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,840
I'll give you all the data

65
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,120
from the lab.

66
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:40,920
Besides that,

67
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,840
I really don't know anything else.

68
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,160
You...

69
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,080
Didn't you die?

70
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:02,360
Jia Yu,

71
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,520
kill him.

72
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,680
You two...

73
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:16,360
So you two are together.

74
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,320
Mr. Zhen.

75
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:20,880
No.

76
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,560
With our relationship,

77
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,680
calling you Mr. Zhen is too formal.

78
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,920
Right?

79
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,040
Brother Era.

80
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,640
You're really not Hao Feng's brother?

81
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,800
That's right.

82
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,280
I am Hao Feng.

83
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:37,200
Impossible.

84
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,440
Impossible.

85
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:40,640
I killed you back then.

86
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,440
I killed you with my own hands.

87
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,320
The one who died at your hands

88
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,920
was my brother Hao Qing.

89
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,720
Now that you finally admit your crimes,

90
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,760
my brother's spirit in heaven

91
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,680
can finally rest in peace.

92
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,800
Your amazing performance just now

93
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,800
is being broadcast live

94
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,840
on all the LED screens in Sunset Glow City.

95
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,480
What do you mean?

96
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:13,040
By the way,

97
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:18,680
And this black diamond heart,

98
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:21,520
on behalf of the victims of the fund blow-up,

99
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:22,880
thank you.

100
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,680
After I died back then,

101
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,440
an old colleague who trusted me

102
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:57,200
stepped forward to claim Hao Feng's ashes.

103
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,360
Since then,

104
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,840
I became his younger brother, Hao Qing.

105
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,560
Back then, the Memory Tree project blew up.

106
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,560
J needed someone to take the blame.

107
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,560
He informed me

108
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,840
to give Zhen Shida an order,

109
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:17,000
to kill you with his own hands.

110
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,640
He killed you.

111
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,920
I don't know when it was.

112
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,840
So that night,

113
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:26,800
I wanted to warn you.

114
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,440
But I didn't expect

115
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:31,920
that it was that night.

116
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:34,760
It's all over.

117
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,520
Actually, at that time,

118
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:38,840
I didn't fully trust you.

119
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:41,800
After the incident,

120
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,840
I thought you betrayed me.

121
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,880
So I did something to you.

122
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,480
A year ago,

123
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,240
in the hospital,

124
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,680
I implanted a chip in you.

125
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,400
The memory observation chip

126
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,600
you developed.

127
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,240
But I will help you take it out.

128
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:05,520
You could have killed me with it at any time,

129
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:06,400
but you didn't.

130
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:09,880
So it doesn't matter anymore.

131
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,320
I've said

132
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,920
I've given my life to you.

133
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,400
Jia Yu,

134
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,560
I hope from now on,

135
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,520
you can live your life to the fullest.

136
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:49,840
How come it's you?
